{"tid":2014790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE穗珍被罵長得醜　舒華「見酸民又來」開嗆","createTime":"2020-05-13T08:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:21:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"326e520ef98ef0889a007259f0f127f075f04053","tid":2014790,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:47:44.000Z","msg":"南韓女團(G)I-DLE（(여자)아이들）成員穗珍4月20日開直播被罵「長得醜」，沒想到另一成員舒華5月10日開直播又發現一樣的惡評，一開始以為是自己搞錯意思懷疑了一下，確認是罵人後直接回嗆：「瘋了是不？」<br />\n<br />\n穗珍4月20日直播發現有人說「沾到海苔了，長得醜（海苔：김，長得醜：못생김）」，瞬間沉默後以嚴肅口吻表示：「你&hellip;現在是在說什麼？」這件事情讓粉絲都相當不滿不捨，結果在23天後又出現了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874008.jpg&h=d9218cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲穗珍直播中被罵長得醜，看起來難過又無奈。（圖／翻攝自(G)I-DLE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n舒華看到「你的臉上有東西，長得醜」，本身是台灣成員，臉上有東西和長得醜又連不上關係就開始思考是不是搞錯意思，再滑回去確認後發現是罵人言語無誤，氣得直接說：「哇！不是上次那個罵穗珍姐姐的吧？瘋了是不？要這樣就出去啊！」<br />\n<br />\n舒華眼神變得兇狠、語氣激動要酸民直接離開就好：「讓人心情很差欸！大家不覺得這種人很過分嗎？」她坦承雖然不會因此而受傷，但別人會難過或是得知這個留言的親朋好友也會心疼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874009.jpg&h=158b8c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲舒華也看見相同類型留言，氣得直接回嘴。（圖／翻攝自(G)I-DLE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n後來一起開直播的成員美延回來後，舒華氣抱怨：「姐姐！我找到罵人的人了！我生氣了！他說什麼臉上有東西、長得醜，那個人最醜！那個人連臉都沒有！」並念出酸民的暱稱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874011.jpg&h=d11583c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美延安慰舒華。（圖／翻攝自(G)I-DLE VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n沒跟上直播的粉絲看了影片後也感到很心疼，但同時也讚賞舒華直率且想保護團員的反應，「自己沒關係但看見這些的朋友和家人會心痛，如果別人被罵也會難過，替他人擔心的這份心意真的很棒很溫暖，直率反應也很帥氣」。<br />\n<br />\n美延正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950715e4ca369aee972a426d6e7af3a044d5e69f","tid":2014790,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"小小批評都接受唔到點做idol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8YBPcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8YBPcr.jpg&h=2de58e33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba7fd3e8bb1a30da9b6d525b0df33ef860f1de1c","tid":2014790,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"快啲做下一個雪莉"},{"pid":"013a326121d0c1a61327b6df79e13863f3216a9d","tid":2014790,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"sure咁睇幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408c80f1cae0f3f7b5ded3a70bff8faa2cd37a48","tid":2014790,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"013a326121d0c1a61327b6df79e13863f3216a9d","tid":2014790,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"sure咁睇幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:52:57.000Z","msg":"唔太覺"},{"pid":"a155752bb1999e5b1fa165d9e028866170989565","tid":2014790,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba7fd3e8bb1a30da9b6d525b0df33ef860f1de1c","tid":2014790,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"快啲做下一個雪莉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"我打斷你條棍"},{"pid":"cd6c4e1bc2dddf5755be85e3b2a3a14e3df1b0fe","tid":2014790,"uid":3405,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"真係樣衰<br />\n唔係黑"},{"pid":"21fd8c9c51be70e7094db8251dd446b96e9ffc9f","tid":2014790,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"408c80f1cae0f3f7b5ded3a70bff8faa2cd37a48","tid":2014790,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"013a326121d0c1a61327b6df79e1